## 4. Business Process Flow

### 4.1 Funding Request Process
1. **Navidoc** mendeteksi kerusakan kapal dan memberikan rekomendasi
2. **Pemilik kapal** menyetujui pengajuan funding melalui platform
3. **NAVI Blockchain** membuat campaign funding dengan detail:
   - Data kapal dan estimasi biaya
   - Syarat cicilan dan bunga
4. **Register fee** dibayar dalam Navicoin atau melalui Point Exchange API
5. Campaign dipublikasikan untuk investor melalui Admin Lending Interface

### 4.2 Investment Process
1. **Investor** melihat daftar campaign melalui Admin Lending Interface
2. Melakukan investasi menggunakan stablecoin atau native coin
3. **STO Token** diterbitkan sesuai proporsi investasi
4. Token dapat:
   - Disimpan untuk mendapat return cicilan
   - Diperjualbelikan di STO Marketplace

### 4.3 Fund Disbursement
1. Setelah target funding tercapai, **NAVI Blockchain** memberikan notifikasi
2. Dana dicairkan langsung ke pemilik kapal atau pihak yang berwenang
3. Perbaikan dilakukan sesuai spesifikasi yang disepakati

### 4.4 Documentation & Repayment
1. Setelah perbaikan selesai, laporan digital dibuat
2. **NFT (ERC-721)** di-mint sebagai dokumentasi permanen
3. **Pemilik kapal** membayar cicilan berkala
4. **Investor** melakukan klaim melalui platform dengan verifikasi STO Token
5. Pembayaran didistribusi pro-rata berdasarkan kepemilikan token

## 5. Technical Specifications

### 5.1 Blockchain Infrastructure
- **Consensus**: DPOS (Delegated Proof of Stake)
- **Compatibility**: EVM/Solana support
- **Native Token**: Navicoin
- **Explorer**: Web-based dengan dark/light mode
- **Validator Network**: Customizable validator system
- **Bridge System**: Cross-chain interoperability

### 5.2 Platform Features

#### For Investors
- **Project Discovery**: Akses daftar campaign funding melalui admin interface
- **Multi-currency Investment**: Support USDT, USDC, SGD stablecoin, dan native coin
- **STO Token Management**: Otomatis receive token setelah investasi
- **Portfolio Monitoring**: Real-time tracking progress proyek dan fund utilization
- **Secondary Trading**: Jual-beli STO token di marketplace
- **Return Claims**: Automated distribution berdasarkan kepemilikan token

#### For Ship Owners (Borrowers)
- **Digital Loan Application**: Submit funding request terintegrasi dengan Navidoc
- **Fund Monitoring**: Dashboard untuk tracking dana dan progress perbaikan
- **Payment Management**: Scheduled repayment melalui smart contract
- **Documentation Access**: View NFT repair reports
- **Point Exchange**: Convert Navi Points ke Navicoin melalui API (rate configurable)

#### Admin Lending Interface
- **Campaign Management**: Create, edit, dan monitor lending campaigns
- **Investor Dashboard**: Comprehensive view untuk investor management
- **Fund Allocation**: Monitor dan manage fund distribution
- **STO Token Oversight**: Track token issuance dan trading activity
- **Analytics & Reporting**: Detailed platform performance metrics
- **User Management**: Investor onboarding dan verification

#### Blockchain Services
- **Smart Contract Verification**: Contract verification dan details
- **Web3 Wallet**: Multi-chain support dengan transaction tracking
- **Custom Token Support**: Add dan manage various tokens
- **Point Exchange API**: Conversion service untuk Navi Points ke Navicoin
- **NFT System**: ERC-721 implementation untuk dokumentasi
- **Bridge Services**: Transfer aset antar blockchain networks

### 5.3 External Integration
- **Navidoc Point System**: Database points di system client
- **Point Exchange API**: Configurable rate conversion (1:1 atau 1000:1)
- **Multi-currency Support**: USDT, USDC, SGD stablecoin
- **Wallet Integration**: Web3 connectivity

### 5.4 Navicoin Utilities
- **Register Fee**: Payment untuk platform registration
- **Transaction Fee Discount**: Pemotongan fee ketika menggunakan Navicoin
- **Point Exchange**: Conversion dari Navi Points dengan configurable rate
- **Investor Benefits**: Enhanced features untuk Navicoin holders

## 6. Project Timeline & Deliverables

### 6.1 Timeline
- **Total Duration**: 50 working days (2 months @ 25 working days/month)
- **Month 1 (Day 1-25)**: Blockchain infrastructure development
  - Blockchain Mainnet dengan DPOS consensus
  - Explorer dan Wallet integration
  - Bridge system dan Smart Contract core
- **Month 2 (Day 26-50)**: Platform development & integration
  - Funding platform dan STO system
  - Marketplace dan NFT implementation
  - Navidoc integration dan testing
- **Maintenance**: 3 months post-launch support

### 6.2 Phase 1 Deliverables (Month 1)
- NAVI Blockchain Mainnet (DPOS consensus)
- Web3 Wallet with multi-chain support
- Blockchain Explorer (web-based)
- Cross-chain Bridge system
- Basic Smart Contract framework
- ICO Website

### 6.3 Phase 2 Deliverables (Month 2)
- Campaign Management System
- STO Token issuance and marketplace
- Admin Lending Interface
- Point Exchange API
- NFT minting system (ERC-721)
- Complete system integration and testing

## 7. Investment Structure

### 7.1 Total Investment
**IDR 600,000,000** (Enam Ratus Juta Rupiah)

### 7.2 Payment Schedule
1. **Down Payment**: IDR 100,000,000 (upon contract signing)
2. **1st Milestone**: IDR 100,000,000 (1 month after project start - Day 25)
3. **2nd Milestone**: IDR 200,000,000 (upon Phase 1 completion - blockchain infrastructure ready)
4. **3rd Milestone**: IDR 100,000,000 (upon project completion - all systems live)
5. **Final Payment**: IDR 100,000,000 (1 month after go-live - maintenance period)

### 7.3 Revenue Streams
- Register fees dalam Navicoin
- Transaction fees dengan discount untuk Navicoin holders
- STO marketplace transaction fees
- Premium features untuk enhanced users

## 8. Risk Management & Security

### 8.1 Technical Security
- Smart contract audit dan verification
- Multi-signature security implementation
- Comprehensive transaction logging
- Cross-chain bridge security protocols

### 8.2 Compliance & Documentation
- KYC integration capability
- Immutable NFT documentation system
- Audit trail untuk semua transaksi
- Regulatory compliance framework

## 9. Success Metrics

### 9.1 Technical KPIs
- Platform uptime > 99.5%
- Transaction processing speed
- Smart contract execution efficiency
- Cross-chain bridge reliability

### 9.2 Business KPIs
- Number of active campaigns
- Total funding volume processed
- Investor participation rate
- STO token trading volume

## 10. Conclusion

Project NAVI menyediakan solusi blockchain komprehensif untuk pembiayaan maritim dengan fokus pada transparansi, efisiensi, dan tokenisasi investasi. Dengan timeline 50 hari kerja dan investasi IDR 600 juta, project ini akan menghasilkan platform yang dapat mendukung ekosistem pembiayaan kapal yang terintegrasi dengan sistem Navidoc client.

Platform ini dirancang untuk skalabilitas dan extensibility, memungkinkan pengembangan fitur tambahan di masa depan sesuai kebutuhan bisnis yang berkembang di sektor maritim Indonesia.

